    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes conventions for using the Session Description Protocol (SDP) described in RFC 2327 for controlling ATM Bearer Connections, and any associated ATM Adaptation Layer (AAL).  The AALs addressed are Type 1, Type 2 and Type 5. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
